    org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulations, org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<java.lang.Long>
    @Entity
@VoDml(id="coords:PixelCoordSystem",
       role=objectType)
public class PixelCoordSystem
extends CoordSys
implements org.ivoa.vodml.jpa.JPAManipulationsForObjectType<java.lang.Long>, org.ivoa.vodml.jaxb.XmlIdManagement
    The PixelCoordSystem provides a complete description of the pixel coordinate space. It SHALL contain one PixelSpace instance describing each pixel axis. objectType: PixelCoordSystem
